Preheat oven to 400 degrees F. Microwave Green Giant RicedÂ® Cauliflower according to package directions. Drain cooked cauliflower in a colander, pressing out as much moisture as possible with paper towels. Stir in egg and cheeses. Spray baking sheet with nonstick cooking spray. Press cauliflower mixture into an 11-inch circle. Bake 25 minutes or until edges are brown and crust is crisp. Top with desired pizza toppings. Bake 8 to 10 minutes.